On [ecopolitology](http://ecopolitology.blogspot.com/), _Tim Hurst_ posts
video clips of [Colbert on World Water
Day](http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Ecopolitology/~3/256225465/colbert-on-
world-water-day.html): “Stephen Colbert celebrates World Water Day – the way
only he could” [Colbert](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stephen_colbert) is a
popular American comedian, satirist and actor.

